<component id="ID_txt04">
  <text><![CDATA[<b><ul><li>A VLAN is an independent LAN network.</li><li>A VLAN allows student and faculty PCs to be separated although they share the same infrastructure.</li><li>A VLAN can be named for easier identification.</li></ul></b>]]></text> 
</component>

